title: About Olamide Adu
text: Olamide Adu is a Data Scientist with background in Forestry and Sustainable Nature Management. He finished his studies in the Euroforester Program from the Swedish University of Agricultural Sciences in 2023. He has a passion for Data Science and is a big lover of the R Language.
